description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection and Gwil Evans Photographic Collection (P 82) Item Number: P082:085 #1453 Image Description: Central School was located between 7th and 8th Streets and Monroe. Building was facing east. The grounds are now part of Corvallis' Central Park. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
